re><span class=\"line\">mybatis:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  config-location: classpath:mybatis-config.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>mybatis-config.xml 添加</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;settings&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;setting name=&quot;logImpl&quot; value=&quot;STDOUT_LOGGING&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/settings&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>不显示的话直接在<code>logback.xml</code>中添加:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;logger name=&quot;xxx.dao&quot; level=&quot;debug&quot;/&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","text":"小技巧当只传入一个变量时, 可以使用_parameter来指代它这里的_parameter就代表传入的parameterType的值 123456<select...","permalink":"/post/Mybatis mapper中的小技巧","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":652,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Mybatis","slug":"Mybatis","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Mybatis.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"经验","slug":"经验","count":7,"path":"api/tags/经验.json"},{"name":"Mybatis","slug":"Mybatis","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Mybatis.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">小技巧</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0-sql-%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">添加 sql 日志</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Weiba","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/24520686?v=4","link":"/","description":"啊 又忘了更新了！","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/xweiba","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","z